data.description: Peacefulness, rural country living at its best!  This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is waiting on you.  Come on over!  It has an open floor plan, spaceous kitchen with a breakfast bar and kitchen dining combo.  It sits on over 1/2 acre of land and is completely fenced.   This lot has lot of potential uses, bring your horse or any other farm animal.  No HOA and low property taxes.  This property is really close to everything, one right turn and you're moments from Bronson or Chiefland.  One left turn and you're moments from Gainesville's Celebration Pointe, I-75 and all of the amenities that Archer Road has to offer.  Call to schedule your tour today; this beauty won't last long.  The Owners are motivated to sell; bring your offer before its gone.
